OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died in his
OL,7,Fbed at a mental health hospital after
OL,8,Fstaff failed to conduct a "proper and
OL,9,Flawful" search of him and other
OL,10,Fpatients on his ward say they're
OL,11,F"devastated" by their loss.
OL,13,FAn inquest into the death of Stefan
OL,14,FBarrie Walker was held at Coroner's
OL,15,FCourt before assistant coroner Edward
OL,16,FRamsay and a jury of 10 members of the
OL,17,Fpublic, concluding on Tuesday, 28 May.
