OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Mr Walker died in
OL,7,Fhis bed at Cefn Coed Hospital in in
OL,8,Fthe middle of the afternoon on 29
OL,9,FJune, 2020 - and concluded that his
OL,10,Fdeath could potentially have been
OL,11,Favoided if hospital staff had searched
OL,12,Fhim and other patients on his ward
OL,13,Ffollowing his return from a brief
OL,14,Fperiod away from the hospital.
OL,16,FThe inquest into Mr Walker's death was
OL,17,Ffirst opened in July 2020 but was
OL,18,Fpaused until May 20, 2024.
