OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FOn the first day of the resumed
OL,7,Finquest, Coroner's Court heard Mr
OL,8,FWalker's family will remember him for
OL,9,Fhis "larger-than-life personality" and
OL,10,F"huge character," and also heard a
OL,11,Fdetailed history of Mr Walker's mental
OL,12,Fhealth diagnoses, along with a recount
OL,13,Fof how Mr Walker came to be under the
OL,14,Fmedical care of Cefn Coed mental
OL,15,Fhealth hospital.
