OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FAfter hearing evidence from medical
OL,7,Fprofessionals and people involved in
OL,8,FMr Walker's care, assistant coroner
OL,9,FEdward Ramsay formally closed the
OL,10,Finquest into Mr Walker's death on
OL,11,FTuesday, May 28, 2024.
OL,13,FThe record of inquest gives Mr
OL,14,FWalker's medical cause of death as
OL,15,F"buprenorphine and flualprazolam
OL,16,Fintoxication and cardiac enlargement"
OL,17,Fand gives an overall conclusion of a
OL,18,Fdrug-related death.
