OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FExplaining the circumstances of Mr
OL,7,FWalker's death, the record reads:
OL,8,F"Stefan died in his bedspace at Cefn
OL,9,FCoed Hospital, on June 29, 2020
OL,10,Fsometime between 3.20pm and 3.45pm."
OL,12,FAn additional statement explains
OL,13,Ffurther: "The death of Stefan Barrie
OL,14,FWalker occurred due to the effects of
OL,15,Fself-administered illicit substances
OL,16,Fin conjunction with an enlarged heart.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
