OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"Stefan had mental health issues which
OL,7,Fwere amplified by his use of illicit
OL,8,Fsubstances. This contributed to his
OL,9,Fintoxication due to the taking of
OL,10,Fthese substances.
OL,12,F"Staff knowledge of search policy
OL,13,Frelating to illicit substances was
OL,14,Finadequate. Escorted ground leave was
OL,15,Fgranted and routine observations were
OL,16,Ftaking place. A full physical health
OL,17,Fcheck took place on June 28, 2020
OL,18,Fconducted by an on-call general
OL,19,Fpractitioner.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
