OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"As a result of this check,
OL,7,Fobservations were recommended at 15-
OL,8,Fminute intervals along with monitoring
OL,9,Fof blood pressure and respiratory
OL,10,Frates for the following six hours.
OL,11,FThese recommendations were followed.
OL,13,F"On June 29, 2020, following review by
OL,14,Fmedical staff, Stefan was exhibiting
OL,15,Fthe same presentations as June 28,
OL,16,F2020, and as such no further actions
OL,17,Fwere deemed to be required apart from
OL,18,Freducing observations from 15-minute
OL,19,Fto 30-minute intervals."
