OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FFurther comments on the record of
OL,7,Finquest stated that if staff had
OL,8,Fchecked Mr Walker and others for drugs
OL,9,Fafter he returned from "ground leave"
OL,10,Faway from the hospital's premises,
OL,11,Fwhich they did not do, Mr Walker's
OL,12,Flife could have potentially been
OL,13,Fsaved.JTo the question "was there a
OL,14,Ffailure to conduct a proper and lawful
OL,15,Fsearch of Stefan and others on Fendrod
OL,16,FWard at Cefn Coed Hospital for illicit
OL,17,Fsubstances following his return from
OL,18,Fground leave on 28 June 2020, in a way
OL,19,Fwhich might potentially have saved his
OL,20,Flife?" the jury stated "yes".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
