OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,FHowever, to the query "was there a
OL,7,Ffailure to carry out a full physical
OL,8,Fhealth check on Stefan, including a
OL,9,Fproperly calculated 'NEWS' score,
OL,10,Fbefore his death on June 29, 2020, in
OL,11,Fa way which might potentially have
OL,12,Fsaved his life?" the jury stated "no".
OL,14,FStefan Walker's mother, Christina
OL,15,FClancy, and his siblings said: "Stefan
OL,16,FWalker was our son and our brother. He
OL,17,Fwas a larger-than-life character with
OL,18,Fa huge personality. Stefan was also
OL,19,Fcomplex and suffered from a number of
OL,20,Fmental health issues.
