OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"On June 29, 2020, whilst under the
OL,7,Fcare of Cefn Coed Hospital, a mental
OL,8,Fhealth facility in Swansea, where he
OL,9,Fwas a residential patient, Stefan died
OL,10,Ffrom an overdose. During the inquest
OL,11,Fat Swansea Coroner's Court, we have
OL,12,Fheard about the failures of those
OL,13,Ftasked with looking after Stefan to
OL,14,Fput measures in place which we feel
OL,15,Fcould have prevented Stefan's death.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
