OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"In particular, the inquest found that
OL,7,Fthere was a failure to conduct a
OL,8,Fproper and lawful search of Stefan and
OL,9,Fothers on Fendrod Ward at Cefn Coed
OL,10,Ffor illicit substances following his
OL,11,Freturn from ground leave on June 28,
OL,12,F2020 in a way which might potentially
OL,13,Fhave saved his life.
OL,15,F"As a family, we have been left
OL,16,Fdevastated and there is a huge hole in
OL,17,Four lives. This should never have
OL,18,Fhappened and had these searches been
OL,19,Fconducted, Stefan may still be with us
OL,20,Ftoday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
