OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"We were pleased to hear that Cefn
OL,7,FCoed have carried out an independent
OL,8,Freview and implemented a number of
OL,9,Fchanges. Sadly, these have come too
OL,10,Flate for Stefan.
OL,12,F"We have also been shocked by the lack
OL,13,Fof mental health facilities. In Wales,
OL,14,Fthere is only one facility that offers
OL,15,Fthe type of treatment that Stefan
OL,16,Fneeded and that is a private hospital.
OL,17,FThere is no provision on the NHS in
OL,18,FWales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
