OL,3,CMan dies in mental health hospital
OL,4,Cafter staff failings
OL,6,F"We are determined that Stefan's death
OL,7,Fwill not have been in vain and are
OL,8,Fdetermined to fight for treatment to
OL,9,Fbe more readily available, so that
OL,10,Fpeople have access to the appropriate
OL,11,Fhelp and no other family needs to go
OL,12,Fthrough what we have. We would like to
OL,13,Fpass on our thanks to our legal team
OL,14,Fand also to the coroner."
